titleStmt.title: An entry from the Journals of Hensley Henson

sourceDesc.bibl: Edited from the manuscripts in the custody of Durham Cathedral Library.

body.p: Lecture II was attended by rather more people, I think; but no member of the Chapter was present besides myself, and only Hine-Haycock of the Minor Canons. If anybody chose to draw certain rather obvious inferences I don't see that anyone could object.
